**T8.4**: Implement error response handling (404, 500, 503)\n   - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/sandbox_delete_test.go -run TestDeleteNotFound -v`\n-- [ ] **T8.5**: Fix `TestDeletionHandler_DeleteMissingSessionID` test (empty sessionID handling)\n+- [x] **T8.5**: Fix `TestDeletionHandler_DeleteMissingSessionID` test (empty sessionID handling)\n   - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/sandbox_delete_test.go -run TestDeleteMissingSessionID -v`\n - [x] **T8.6**: Implement `HealthHandler` with `/healthz` and `/readyz`\n   - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/health_test.go -v`\n - [x] **T8.7**: Implement `HealthChecker` interface\n","filediff":{"file":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-007/tasks.md","before":"# AR-007 — K8s Reconciler 控制器 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-007 — K8s Reconciler 控制器 |\n| Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | L |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Core Types & Configuration (ST-1)\n\n- [x] **T1.1**: Define error types (`ValidationError`, `NotFoundError`, `InternalError`, `ServiceUnavailableError`, `ConflictError`)\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager -run TestErrorTypes -v`\n- [x] **T1.2**: Define `ErrorResponse` and `SuccessResponse` structs\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/types_test.go -v`\n- [x] **T1.3**: Implement `HandleError` function for HTTP error responses\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/types_test.go -run TestHandleError -v`\n- [x] **T1.4**: Define `DeletionReason` enum constants\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go -run TestDetermineDeletionReason -v`\n- [x] **T1.5**: Define `Config` struct with HTTP server parameters\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/config_test.go -run TestDefaultConfig -v`\n- [x] **T1.6**: Define `LifecycleConfig` struct with TTL/idle timeout settings\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go -run TestDefaultLifecycleConfig -v`\n- [x] **T1.7**: Define constants (SandboxGVR, SandboxClaimGVR, labels, annotations)\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/defaults_test.go -run TestGVRConstants -v`\n\n### Phase 2: Store Implementation (ST-2)\n\n- [x] **T2.1**: Implement `Store` interface with CRUD methods\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/store_test.go -v`\n- [x] **T2.2**: Implement `MemoryStore` with sync.RWMutex\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/store_test.go -run TestMemoryStore -v`\n- [x] **T2.3**: Implement `ListExpiredSandboxes` with time-based filtering\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/store_test.go -run TestListExpired -v`\n- [x] **T2.4**: Implement `ListInactiveSandboxes` with LastActivity filtering\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/store_test.go -run TestListInactive -v`\n- [x] **T2.5**: Implement expiration index for efficient cleanup\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/store_test.go -run TestExpirationIndex -v`\n\n### Phase 3: Kubernetes Client (ST-3)\n\n- [x] **T3.1**: Implement `K8sClient` struct with dynamic/client-go clients\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/k8s_client_test.go -run TestNewK8sClient -v`\n- [x] **T3.2**: Implement `ClientCache` for token-scoped dynamic clients\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/k8s_client_test.go -run TestClientCache -v`\n- [x] **T3.3**: Implement `StartInformers` and `WaitForCacheSync`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/k8s_client_test.go -run TestInformers -v`\n- [x] **T3.4**: Implement `PodLister` accessor\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/k8s_client_test.go -run TestPodLister -v`\n- [x] **T3.5**: Implement `Informers` wrapper struct\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/informers_test.go -v`\n- [x] **T3.6**: Fix `TestInformers_WaitForCacheSyncTimeout` test failure\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/informers_test.go -run TestInformers_WaitForCacheSyncTimeout -v`\n\n### Phase 4: Lifecycle Manager (ST-4)\n\n- [x] **T4.1**: Implement `SandboxLifecycleManager` struct\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go -run TestNewSandboxLifecycleManager -v`\n- [x] **T4.2**: Implement `DeleteSandbox` with K8s resource deletion\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go -run TestDeleteSandbox_Success -v`\n- [x] **T4.3**: Implement `ForceDeleteSandbox` with gracePeriod=0\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go -run TestForceDelete -v`\n- [x] **T4.4**: Implement `IsExpired` time check\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go -run TestIsExpired -v`\n- [x] **T4.5**: Implement `IsIdleExpired` with LastActivity check\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go -run TestIsIdleExpired -v`\n- [x] **T4.6**: Implement `GetSandbox` and `UpdateSandboxStatus`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go -run TestGetSandbox -v`\n- [x] **T4.7**: Implement `determineDeletionReason` logic\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go -run TestDetermineDeletionReason -v`\n- [x] **T4.8**: Implement `handleDeleteError` for K8s API errors\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go -run TestHandleDeleteError -v`\n\n### Phase 5: Garbage Collector (ST-5)\n\n- [x] **T5.1**: Implement `GarbageCollector` struct with interval/timeout\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector_test.go -run TestNewGarbageCollector -v`\n- [x] **T5.2**: Implement `runLoop` background ticker loop\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector_test.go -run TestStartStop -v`\n- [x] **T5.3**: Implement `runOnce` batch cleanup logic\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector_test.go -run TestRunOnce -v`\n- [x] **T5.4**: Implement expired sandbox cleanup (MaxDurationReached)\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector_test.go -run TestRunOnce_Expired -v`\n- [x] **T5.5**: Implement idle sandbox cleanup (IdleTimeout)\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector_test.go -run TestRunOnce_Inactive -v`\n- [x] **T5.6**: Implement `GCBatchSize` limit (16 items)\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector_test.go -run TestRunOnce_Limit -v`\n- [x] **T5.7**: Implement concurrent-safe cleanup\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector_test.go -run TestConcurrentRunOnce -v`\n\n### Phase 6: HTTP Server & Router (ST-6)\n\n- [x] **T6.1**: Implement `HTTPServer` struct with graceful shutdown\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/server_test.go -run TestStartStop -v`\n- [x] **T6.2**: Implement `NewHTTPServer` and `NewHTTPServerWithClients`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/server_test.go -run TestNewHTTPServer -v`\n- [x] **T6.3**: Implement `RegisterHandler` method\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/server_test.go -run TestRegisterHandler -v`\n- [x] **T6.4**: Implement `Start` with error channel\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/integration_test.go -run TestStartStopLifecycle -v`\n- [x] **T6.5**: Implement `Stop` with context timeout\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/server_test.go -run TestStop -v`\n- [x] **T6.6**: Implement `GracefulShutdown` signal handler\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/server_test.go -run TestGracefulShutdown -v`\n- [x] **T6.7**: Implement `Router` chi.Router wrapper\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/router_test.go -v`\n\n### Phase 7: Middleware (ST-7)\n\n- [x] **T7.1**: Implement `RecoveryMiddleware` panic handler\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/recovery_test.go -v`\n- [x] **T7.2**: Implement `LoggingMiddleware` request logger\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/logging_test.go -v`\n- [x] **T7.3**: Implement `CORSMiddleware` with config\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/cors_test.go -v`\n- [x] **T7.4**: Verify middleware chain order (Recovery → Logging → CORS)\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/integration_test.go -run TestMiddlewareChain -v`\n\n### Phase 8: Handlers (ST-8)\n\n- [x] **T8.1**: Implement `DeletionHandler` struct\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/sandbox_delete_test.go -run TestDeletionHandler_Register -v`\n- [x] **T8.2**: Implement DELETE `/v1/agent-runtime/sessions/{sessionId}`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/sandbox_delete_test.go -run TestDeleteSuccess -v`\n- [x] **T8.3**: Implement DELETE `/v1/code-interpreter/sessions/{sessionId}`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/sandbox_delete_test.go -run TestDeleteCodeInterpreter -v`\n- [x] **T8.4**: Implement error response handling (404, 500, 503)\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/sandbox_delete_test.go -run TestDeleteNotFound -v`\n- [ ] **T8.5**: Fix `TestDeletionHandler_DeleteMissingSessionID` test (empty sessionID handling)\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/sandbox_delete_test.go -run TestDeleteMissingSessionID -v`\n- [x] **T8.6**: Implement `HealthHandler` with `/healthz` and `/readyz`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/health_test.go -v`\n- [x] **T8.7**: Implement `HealthChecker` interface\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/health_test.go -run TestHealthChecker -v`\n\n### Phase 9: Integration Tests (ST-9)\n\n- [x] **T9.1**: E2E health endpoint test\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/integration_test.go -run TestE2EHealthz -v`\n- [x] **T9.2**: E2E readiness endpoint test\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/integration_test.g