n` enum constants\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go -run TestDetermineDeletionReason -v`\n- [x] **T1.5**: Define `Config` struct with HTTP server parameters\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/config_test.go -run TestDefaultConfig -v`\n- [x] **T1.6**: Define `LifecycleConfig` struct with TTL/idle timeout settings\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go -run TestDefaultLifecycleConfig -v`\n- [x] **T1.7**: Define constants (SandboxGVR, SandboxClaimGVR, labels, annotations)\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/defaults_test.go -run TestGVRConstants -v`\n\n### Phase 2: Store Implementation (ST-2)\n\n- [x] **T2.1**: Implement `Store` interface with CRUD methods\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/store_test.go -v`\n- [x] **T2.2**: Implement `MemoryStore` with sync.RWMutex\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/store_test.go -run TestMemoryStore -v`\n- [x] **T2.3**: Implement `ListExpiredSandboxes` with time-based filtering\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/store_test.go -run TestListExpired -v`\n- [x] **T2.4**: Implement `ListInactiveSandboxes` with LastActivity filtering\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/store_test.go -run TestListInactive -v`\n- [x] **T2.5**: Implement expiration index for efficient cleanup\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/store_test.go -run TestExpirationIndex -v`\n\n### Phase 3: Kubernetes Client (ST-3)\n\n- [x] **T3.1**: Implement `K8sClient` struct with dynamic/client-go clients\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/k8s_client_test.go -run TestNewK8sClient -v`\n- [x] **T3.2**: Implement `ClientCache` for token-scoped dynamic clients\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/k8s_client_test.go -run TestClientCache -v`\n- [x] **T3.3**: Implement `StartInformers` and `WaitForCacheSync`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/k8s_client_test.go -run TestInformers -v`\n- [x] **T3.4**: Implement `PodLister` accessor\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/k8s_client_test.go -run TestPodLister -v`\n- [x] **T3.5**: Implement `Informers` wrapper struct\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/informers_test.go -v`\n- [x] **T3.6**: Fix `TestInformers_WaitForCacheSyncTimeout` test failure\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/informers_test.go -run TestInformers_WaitForCacheSyncTimeout -v`\n\n### Phase 4: Lifecycle Manager (ST-4)\n\n- [x] **T4.1**: Implement `SandboxLifecycleManager` struct\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go -run TestNewSandboxLifecycleManager -v`\n- [x] **T4.2**: Implement `DeleteSandbox` with K8s resource deletion\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go -run TestDeleteSandbox_Success -v`\n- [x] **T4.3**: Implement `ForceDeleteSandbox` with gracePeriod=0\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go -run TestForceDelete -v`\n- [x] **T4.4**: Implement `IsExpired` time check\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go -run TestIsExpired -v`\n- [x] **T4.5**: Implement `IsIdleExpired` with LastActivity check\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go -run TestIsIdleExpired -v`\n- [x] **T4.6**: Implement `GetSandbox` and `UpdateSandboxStatus`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go -run TestGetSandbox -v`\n- [x] **T4.7**: Implement `determineDeletionReason` logic\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go -run TestDetermineDeletionReason -v`\n- [x] **T4.8**: Implement `handleDeleteError` for K8s API errors\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go -run TestHandleDeleteError -v`\n\n### Phase 5: Garbage Collector (ST-5)\n\n- [x] **T5.1**: Implement `GarbageCollector` struct with interval/timeout\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector_test.go -run TestNew